reviewText: At last a very nice series on the Navy activities and a good excursion on nice seas. Very realistic, don't be too attached to some of the characters.
even better, it is a great  show which  a miss a lot ! they should have not stop at season five

I enjoyed watching this and what a shame that season 5 is the last ever season ever made. Really taking in the seas around the pacific which is great to see. What they do and why.
I think that this is really cool job to do.

GREAT! Sea Patrol is one of the best shows there is.  I bought a DVD player to be able to accept the format and plan to purchase every season available.  I already own 1-4.  I hear season 5 will be their last but hope they will reconsider and there will be more.  ABSOLUTELY LOVE SEA PATROL.
